com.nokia.maps.routing.enums

Interface RouteFeature

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    RouteLinkFlag

    public interface RouteFeature
    This interface defines the route features. Route features can be used to define special conditions on the calculated route. The user can weight each feature with positive or negative weights, see type RouteFeatureWeight.
    See Also:
    RouteFeatureWeight
